      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHATTANOOGA (1) shapes well for this backing up a quick 25.88 win with success at Sandown over 515m last time, recording 29.69. Clocking fast times and looks a key chance again here. MAGIC SNOWDROP (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at Shepparton over 450m behind Doongalla Rocket (25.85) in a Grade 4/5. Worth another chance. SON OF WITCHY (7) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 24.00 beating Nala's Ghost. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature again. DAVE (3) is right in the mix.",
